<div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
        <h1>Welcome to DDD East Anglia!</h1>
        <p>
            @Html.DDDEastAnglia() will be coming to Cambridge on 29 June 2013 at the Hauser Forum. Like all DDD community events,
            @Html.DDDEastAnglia() is free to attend, funded entirely through the generosity of our sponsors. Please 
            @Html.ActionLink("get in touch", MVC.Home.Contact()) if you would like to join other supporters of the UK .NET community
            by sponsoring @Html.DDDEastAnglia().
        </p>
        <p>
            Registration will open nearer to the date, but we invite you to take a look around the site to whet your appetite for what
            promises to be a fantastic event!  Why not <a href="http://www.twitter.com/dddeastanglia">follow us on Twitter</a> to get
